title: Native Instruments The Mouth v1.3.0 MacOSX-R2R
description:
PlatenseSoul | R2R | 2014.03.12 | 4.3 MB

THE MOUTH! Designed to generate melodies and harmonies out of whatever audio material you feed it, THE MOUTH is a unique and exciting way to get creative results on the fly. Sing, beatbox or send a drum loop into it and THE MOUTH comes to life as a tweakable synthesizer, bass, vocoder or talkbox-like effect. A playful interface provides you with plenty of room to shape your results as you go.

Release Info:

Installer created by me. The original files were extracted from the Windows release of R2R.

1) Extract.
2) Mount the image and install.
3) Use it with a k'ed version of Reaktor 5.9.0 for Mac.
